*libevdev-1.4 (27 Mar 2015)

  27 Mar 2015; Chí-Thanh Christopher Nguyễn <chithanh@gentoo.org>
  +libevdev-1.4.ebuild, -libevdev-0.6-r1.ebuild, -libevdev-0.6.ebuild,
  -libevdev-1.2.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. Remove old.

  14 Mar 2015; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> libevdev-1.3.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #530652

  06 Mar 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> libevdev-1.3.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #530652).

  02 Mar 2015; Yixun Lan <dlan@gentoo.org> libevdev-1.3.ebuild:
  add arm64 support, tested on A53 board

  24 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libevdev-1.3.ebuild:
  Stable for alpha, wrt bug #530652

  23 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libevdev-1.3.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #530652

  22 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libevdev-1.3.ebuild:
  Stable for ia64, wrt bug #530652

  21 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libevdev-1.3.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc64, wrt bug #530652

  20 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libevdev-1.3.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #530652

  19 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libevdev-1.3.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #530652

  18 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libevdev-1.3.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #530652

  25 Jan 2015; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> libevdev-0.6.ebuild,
  libevdev-0.6-r1.ebuild, libevdev-1.2.1.ebuild, libevdev-1.3.ebuild:
  Add ~sparc/~sh wrt #487944

